  "subject": "New position chartered in Thingalog org 2026-05-27: thingalog-performance-engineer (purely performance + caching + cost; SHOULD priority; currently vacant) — surfacing as potential canonical roledef-shape candidate (single derivation only; one-of-three threshold; file-and-watch)",

